*Priča se* da je ona preselila u drugu zemlju. (It is said that she moved to another country.)

*Pričala* je o njenim uspesima. (She was talking about her successes.)

*Pričam* o putovanju po svetu. (I am talking about travelling around the world.)

*Pričali* smo o našim namerama. (We were talking about our intentions.)

*Pričao* mi je o najboljim prijateljima. (He was telling me about his best friends.)

*Pričaju* da oni idu u Pariz. (They are saying that they are going to Paris.)